0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 명령문으로 파드(POD)생성</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>명령문을 사용해 Pod 매니페스트 파일을 생성한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">root@controlplane ~ ➜  k run nginx-pod --image<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>nginx:alpine --dry-run<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>client -o yaml <span class=\"token operator\">></span> nginx-pod.yaml</code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>생성된 매니페스트 파일 내용이 맞는지 확인한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">root@controlplane ~ ➜  <span class=\"token function\">vi</span> nginx-pod.yaml\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token operator\">==</span>\n\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Pod\nmetadata:\n  creationTimestamp: null\n  labels:\n    run: nginx-pod\n  name: nginx-pod\nspec:\n  containers:\n  - image: nginx:alpine\n    name: nginx-pod\n    resources: <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  dnsPolicy: ClusterFirst\n  restartPolicy: Always\nstatus: <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>매니페스트 파일을 이용해 파드를 생성한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">root@controlplane ~ ➜  k create -f nginx-pod.yaml \npod/nginx-pod created</code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>파드가 제대로 생성되었는지 확인한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">root@controlplane ~ ➜  k get pods\nNAME        READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE\nnginx-pod   <span class=\"token number\">1</span>/1     Running   <span class=\"token number\">0</span>          12s</code></pre></div>\n<p><br/><br/></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-참고-url\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-url\" aria-label=\"3 참고 url permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 참고 URL</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>kubectl cheat sheet: <a href=\"https://kubernetes.io/ko/docs/reference/kubectl/cheatsheet/\">https://kubernetes.io/ko/docs/reference/kubectl/cheatsheet/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>","frontmatter":{"date":"May 17, 2022","title":"쿠버네티스(Kubernetes) CKA 모의고사 1.1 - 기본적인 파드(POD) 생성하기","categories":"데브옵스","author":"jinnypark9393","emoji":"🔧"},"fields":{"slug":"/220517-kubernetes-cka-mock-exam-1-01/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://jinnypark9393.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"jinnypark9393/jinnypark9393.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/220517-kubernetes-cka-mock-exam-1-02/","nextSlug":"/220517-kubernetes-cka-mock-exam-1-12/","prevSlug":"/220517-kubernetes-cka-mock-exam-1-01/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}